great game, always has been. team play, tactical play and very competitive.

I purchased and downloaded this game and.....

There I was,  on a Global Offensive..Attempting to Counter-Strike the opposition via round based gunplay and tactics.

Although, my Offensive engagement seemed at times a little outdated, the actions were thoroughly engaging and provided a framework to potentially spend hours and hours decimating my opponents one pixel at a time.... lliterally.. like, one pixel = one opponent...

Graphics and outdated looks/feel aside... great gameplay!
